Detailed Description

Describes the encoding parameters like color format, size and quality level.

Member Enumeration Documentation

enum PngEncoder::EncodingParameters::EncodingFormat
 

Encoding format of the PNG image. The encoding format can be changed by PngEncoder::SetEncodingFormat. Currently only the RgbFormat is supported.
